%= include 'navigation.inc', active => 'about'

<!-- about team -->
<section id="team" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title text-center">About Us</h2>
    <p>The Ballarat Hackerspace is modeled on an <a href="http://hackerspaces.org/">international community of like minded spaces</a> that started in Germany back in 1995. It supports and encourages Science, Technology, Engineering, Art and Mathematics culture in the Ballarat region by providing a physical space for residents to meet, interact, create and innovate.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="donations" class="section section-highlight">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="title text-center">Donations</h2>
    <p>The Ballarat Hackerspace is a registered non-profit volunteer run organisation. We are entirely funded by our members and the generous donations of our sponsors. If you would like to support the work of the Ballarat Hackerspace Association to help with the running costs of the Hackerspace (e.g. rent, consumables, workshops, etc.) then any donation would be gladly accepted and put to good use!</p>
    <p>Donations to the association can be made via bank deposit to:</p>
    <blockquote>
      Account Name: Ballarat Hackerspace Inc<br/>
      BSB : 193-879<br/>
      Account No: 468 349 494
    </blockquote>
    <p>Or you can donate Bitcoin or Bitcoin Cash to the following address:</p>
    <blockquote>
      <a href="https://blockchain.info/address/1BHackHL8bYsGb5PBaXURAot2ymLZtRpTo">1BHackHL8bYsGb5PBaXURAot2ymLZtRpTo</a>
    </blockquote>
    <p>If instead of money you have time to donate then please
      <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
  </div><!--//container-->
</section>

